        <Parent_String>balustrade and railing components [300073693], balustrades, railings and their components [300073692], barrier elements [300001988], barriers and barrier elements [300163880], architectural elements [300000885], components by specific context [300241584], components (objects parts) [300241583], Components (hierarchy name) [300241490], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
